about.summary: A collection of tweening / easing functions

name: pytweening
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "1.0.3" %}
{% set name = "PyTweening" %}

package:
  name: pytweening
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  fn: PyTweening-{{ version }}.zip
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.zip
  sha256: 4b608a570f4dccf2201e898f643c2a12372eb1d71a3dbc7e778771b603ca248b

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: python setup.py install  --single-version-externally-managed --record=record.txt

requirements:
  build:
    - python
    - setuptools
  run:
    - python

test:
  imports:
    - pytweening

about:
  home: https://github.com/asweigart/pytweening
  license: BSD 3-Clause
  license_family: BSD
  # https://github.com/asweigart/pytweening/pull/3
  #license_file: LICENSE.txt
  summary: A collection of tweening / easing functions

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - jschueller
